 Wireless Ad Hoc
1.	Configure Wireless Hotspot
a.	Click Wireless Icon
b.	Advanced
c.	Create Hotpot
d.	Connect vis SSH(tricky part)
Connecting vis SSH
1.	Link: https://www.howtogeek.com/768053/how-to-ssh-into-your-raspberry-pi/
2.	Run raspi-config as SU
3.	Enable SSH (search a bit for it)
4.	Edit sshd_config file to disallow root login
5.	Adduser for connecting
6.	Restart ssh
7.	Connect with ssh user@ip.add.re.ss
8.	Blood makes the grass grow, Huzzah! 
